<li id="cite_note-:3-90"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-:3_90-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">McGregor, Susan. 2014. “DIGITAL SECURITY AND SOURCE PROTECTION FOR JOURNALISTS.” <i>Tow Center for Digital Journalism A Tow/Knight.</i>pp. 03–88. Retrieved (<a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="https://academiccommons.columbia.edu/doi/10.7916/D89P3D4M">https://academiccommons.columbia.edu/doi/10.7916/D89P3D4M</a>).</span>
